@doc Usage:

```
  slime:validate(#{
    name => slime_misc:and([
      fun slime_misc:binary/1,
      slime_misc:length({between, {6, 250}})
    ]),
    role => slime_misc:and([
      fun slime_misc:binary/1,
      slime_misc:compare({in, [<<"admin">>, <<"user">>]}),
      fun(Value) -> {ok, binary_to_atom(Value)} end
    ])
  },
  , #{
    "name" => "user name",
    <<"role">> => "admin"
  }) = {ok, #{name => <<"user name">>, role => admin}}
'''